original: Jagenburg, Hans Rudolf, ingenjör, Borås, f. 18/8/94 i Kinnarumma, Älvsb. 1., av dir. Rudolf Otto J. o. Ida Pet- 31 tersson. G. 22 m. Gudrun Håkansson. Barn: Siv f. 24, Anine-Beate 28. — Stud:ex. v. Örebro tekn. .sk. 19, stud. i Amerika, Tyskl., Frankr. o. Tjecko-slov. 19-22. Res. t. Amerika 37 o. 46. Ing. v. Borås Wäfveri A-B, avd. tryckeriet, s’ed. 21, avd xhef S’ed. 36. Led. av styr. f. Borås Wäfveri A-B sed. 38. Erövrat ett flert. sv. mästersk. i allm. idr.
translated: Jagenburg, Hans Rudolf, engineer, Borås, b. 18/8/94 in Kinnarumma, Älvsb. Co., son of director Rudolf Otto J. and Ida Pettersson. Married on 22 with Gudrun Håkansson. Children: Siv b. 24, Anine-Beate b. 28. - Student from Örebro Technical School in 19, studied in America, Germany, France and Czechoslovakia from 19-22. Traveled to America in 37 and 46. Engineer at Borås Wäfveri A-B, printing department, since 21 and department head since 36. Member of the board for Borås Wäfveri A-B since 38. Won several Swedish championships in sports.
